FBIS4-58675 "drnes088_j_94011" FBIS-NES-94-088 Daily Report 5 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Fighting Continues; Airport Bombed; Calls for Peace Made Fighting Continues; Airport Bombed; Calls for Peace Made `All-Out' Fighting in Provinces NC0505143994 Paris AFP in English 1420 GMT 5 May 94 NC0505143994 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Sanaa, 5 May (AFP) -- All-out fighting erupted Thursday in Yemen between rival troops in seven provinces as five southern warplanes were shot down, a northern military spokesman said here. The spokesman told the official news agency SABA' that southern forces from Aden had suffered heavy losses in clashes with northern troops in seven of Yemen's 17 provinces.
